data.description: OPEN HOUSE, Sunday Jan 28th 1-3 pm.    Several renovations to this home on a cul-de-sac including New Kitchen and Bathroom cabinets, SS Appliances incl. Air Fryer in Range, Recessed Electric Fireplace, Lighting, Shiplap Ceiling, Vinyl plank flooring, water heater & electrical!  NEW DECK 2023. New 50 year roof and 25 year SOLAR panels - July 2022  Average electric bills under $10.00 a month! (Solar panels Convey with home.) Radiant shield and solar fan in attic. HVAC(2016) with UV-C light installed in 2022. (All duct work was cleaned at time of UV-C light installation) Located in the sought after Forest School District. built-in office Desk and Piano Convey.
